{"atom_id": "ig34_p0455_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 455, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§10.E Appendix E: Revision History", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "5.4 | Subject Disease Milestones (SM) | Updated CDISC notes for USUBJID for consistency.", "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.7", "ts": "2026-04-29T14:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0455_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 455, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "§10.E Appendix E: Revision History", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "5.5 | Subject Visits (SV) | This domain had been considered for moving to Events, but the decision after public review was to keep it as a Subject Visits domain at this time. Now contains visits that did not occur as well as those that did occur. Information was added about contacts with subjects which may not have been designated as \"visits\" in the protocol. New variables were added: SVPRESP, SVOCCUR, SVREASOC, SVCNTMOD, SVEPCHGI.", "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.7", "ts": "2026-04-29T14:00:00Z"}}
